<img id="photo121" onclick="expGallery211.growPicture('21','1');expGallery211.trackGalleryImg('Attorney General Eric Holder announces resignation')" class="cnnArticleBoxImage" width="640" height="360" border="0" src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/140925165202-02-holder-0925-horizontal-gallery.jpg" alt="Photos: Eric Holder resigns"/>
<cite id="cite121" class="expCaption"><span>Photos: Eric Holder resigns</span></cite>
</div>
