<div class="cnn_stryspcvbx"><div class="cnn_stryspcvbxcntr"><div class="cnn_stryscbx1">
<div><a href="/2014/09/25/politics/eric-holder-resignation/index.html?iid=article_sidebar">Attorney General Eric Holder announces resignation</a></div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 5:20 PM EDT, Thu September 25, 2014
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
<a href="/2014/09/25/politics/eric-holder-resignation/index.html?iid=article_sidebar"><img src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/140925105946-05-holder-t1-video-tease.jpg" alt="" border="0" height="68" width="120"/></a>
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx4">Attorney General Eric Holder announced that he will resign after six years at the helm of the Justice Department.</div>
<div class="cnn_clear"></div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="cnn_stryspcvbx"><div class="cnn_stryspcvbxcntr"><div class="cnn_stryscbx1">
<div><a href="/2014/09/25/politics/eric-holder-legacy/index.html?iid=article_sidebar">Eric Holder's legacy</a></div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 4:52 PM EDT, Thu September 25, 2014
</div>
